OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A French tourist who has been held in  
OL,6, Iran since 2020 charged with espionage 
OL,7, has gone on trial, his lawyers say.    
OL,9,FBenjamin Briere, 36, was arrested after
OL,10,Fflying a drone near the                
OL,11,FIran-Turkmenistan border.              
OL,13,FIf convicted he could receive a jail   
OL,14,Fterm, though his Iran-based lawyer has 
OL,15,Fimplied authorities are considering    
OL,16,Fincluding him in a prisoner exchange.  
OL,18,FMr Briere has been on hunger strike    
OL,19,Fsince December, leaving him very weak, 
OL,20,Fanother of his lawyers has said.       
